```

# Output

```md
- A list item.
<details><summary>Summary</summary>
<p>
- A list item.

</p>
</details>
- A list item.
<blockquote>

<p>quoted sentence1<br>
quoted sentence2</p>
</blockquote>
- indented html is formatted as it is
  <blockquote>asdf</blockquote>
```
